Definition: the branch of theology that is concerned with such final things as death and Last Judgment
Example: Heaven and Hell; the ultimate destiny of humankind
Synonyms: adj, pert, eschatological, noun, person, eschatologist, theology, the, branch, of, that, is, concerned, with, such, final, things, as, death, and, Last, Judgment, Heaven, Hell, ultimate, destiny, humankind
Category: noun.cognition
